original_title: Pro Wrestling's Future Legend: Cheerleader Melissa
overview: Both athletic and beautiful, Cheerleader Melissa has quickly gained a large fan following since entering the arena of pro wrestling. This program features some exciting bone-crushing action, as Melissa takes on both male and female opponents. In seven matches, the second-generation wrestler and future legend shows once and for all that her awe-inspiring strength and remarkable fighting skills equal or surpass her good looks.
title: Pro Wrestling's Future Legend: Cheerleader Melissa
